]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it's a moot point really as none of the three veterans will stand on top of the podium at Roland Garros as that honour is going toCarlos Alcaraz.\", \"from\": 411, \"to\": 560, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 552, \"end\": 559, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.926155238576663e-18, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a moot point\", \"from\": 420, \"to\": 432}, {\"ngram\": \"none\", \"from\": 443, \"to\": 447}, {\"ngram\": \"the three veterans\", \"from\": 451, \"to\": 469}, {\"ngram\": \"top\", \"from\": 484, \"to\": 487}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 491, \"to\": 501}, {\"ngram\": \"Roland Garros\", \"from\": 505, \"to\": 518}, {\"ngram\": \"that honour\", \"from\": 522, \"to\": 533}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 21-year-old Spaniard is fresh from winning his fourth grand slam when he beat Djokovic in straight sets at Wimbledon just a couple of weeks ago and that followed victory in theFrench Open.\", \"from\": 562, \"to\": 754, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 578, \"end\": 586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"score\": 0.9412103852198216, \"rank\": 0.06246078139818632, \"text\": \"Spaniard\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his fourth grand slam\", \"from\": 609, \"to\": 630}, {\"ngram\": \"Djokovic\", \"from\": 644, \"to\": 652}, {\"ngram\": \"straight sets\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 669}, {\"ngram\": \"Wimbledon\", \"from\": 673, \"to\": 682}, {\"ngram\": \"weeks\", \"from\": 700, \"to\": 705}, {\"ngram\": \"victory\", \"from\": 728, \"to\": 735}, {\"ngram\": \"theFrench Open\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 753}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is destined to be the next tennis superstar and could be just as dashing and dominant as Roger Federer, Nadal and Djokovic in their pomp, and he's already the sport's glamorous new poster boy.\", \"from\": 756, \"to\": 951, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 848, \"end\": 861, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Federer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Roger Federer\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Federer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Roger_Federer\"}, {\"begin\": 863, \"end\": 868, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4565995771488486e-16, \"text\": \"Nadal\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rafael_Nadal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the next tennis superstar\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 802}, {\"ngram\": \"Djokovic\", \"from\": 873, \"to\": 881}, {\"ngram\": \"their pomp\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 895}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport's glamorous new poster boy\", \"from\": 914, \"to\": 950}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He returns to his favoured clay court at Roland Garros seeking to extend his remarkable run and it is difficult to see anyone standing in his way.\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 1099, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his favoured clay court\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 990}, {\"ngram\": \"Roland Garros\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1007}, {\"ngram\": \"his remarkable run\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1044}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1078}, {\"ngram\": \"his way\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1098}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alcaraz simply has to be backed at 7/4 with Bet Victor, Sky Bet and StarSports, even though it is a skinny price.\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1214, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1101, \"end\": 1108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.92615523857666